{"tid":336294,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲可以送唔睇既動畫bluray比我","createTime":"2017-07-26T10:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T15:41:52.000Z","uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca2e63ab91a255de14b1a268c1a73b9c1bc6a8de","tid":336294,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:24:34.000Z","msg":"利申左先 屋企冇乜錢買bluray碟 <br />\n但好好彩係垃圾站執到部用到既藍光player<br />\n唔係話窮到穿窿 但就算有多餘錢都唔係去買碟<br />\n<br />\n我下年想學睇動畫 睇動畫上網down又好似侵權<br />\n但屋企唔太多錢 千幾蚊食到半個月<br />\n<br />\n所以睇下有冇巴絲有d全新/睇到既bluray碟可以讓出黎 <br />\n送比我就當然最好 但如果係平平地放比我我都唔介意嫁 <br />\n希望各位巴絲幫幫忙 如果有野想交換可以問下我 <br />\n<br />\n祝各位下個月新年快樂 今年願望除大家身體健康之外<br />\n其中一個細細地ge願望就係想自己有盒bluray碟<br />\n同學下睇動畫 等自己生活冇咁頹廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6272405e017244cdc06e7d34e5e6f3bc00f5d813","tid":336294,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有既可以留個tg架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e0b844b715b96110f64052ef34c0969f47f61c","tid":336294,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:27:14.000Z","msg":"你到底一篇文可以出幾多個version?"},{"pid":"2e65a0fb6269aaaeacacd489e719593d515b8af1","tid":336294,"uid":21456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:29:12.000Z","msg":"聽講會員瀧三訂左成打你的名字bd<br />\n可以問下佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc07fc847283a45ebb8dacf66192c54a12253de","tid":336294,"uid":21456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T13:41:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講會員瀧三訂左成打你的名字bd<br />\n可以問下佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f25ed22e6df05f0f4b2dfa862b9085b3f4cc4040","tid":336294,"uid":80461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T15:37:13.000Z","msg":"連登都是翻版網站，勸依